replies.body:
Please dont remove Raptor Cloak please. At least add it to either {{item:3800}}  or {{item:3742}} . Many top lane users such as singed and darius benefit from the item in tough matchups and others as well. 
A item that you should look into removing should be {{item:2419}} 

Also while we are at {{item:3800}} you should remove {{item:3024}} from its build path and replace it with partors cloak. None of its users benefit from the mana that it gives, only the cooldown reduction and armor.
